Description: TMJOs popup launcher + dock (Rust)
 Suite TMJOs de UX shell: dois binários compartilhando código.
 .
   * tmjmenu — popup search launcher (Super+Space). Lista apps XDG,
     busca fuzzy por nome/comment/keywords.
   * tmjdock — dock bottom-center no painel INTERNO do laptop
     (eDP/LVDS/DSI). Botão TMJOs com gradient cyan/magenta + pinned
     apps. Wayland nativo via gtk4-layer-shell (Recommends), fallback
     X11 hints.
 .
 Reescrito em Rust + gtk4-rs + libadwaita em v2.0.0 (era Python +
 PyGObject). Binary statically linked, single-binary distribution.
 .
 gir1.2-gtk4layershell-1.0 + libgtk4-layer-shell0 são Recommends —
 sem eles, tmjdock cai pro fallback X11 sem quebrar.
